# MalApi

## Instructions

-   Create an app at https://myanimelist.net/apiconfig (May want to use http://localhost:8000/callback)
-   Place the MAL_CLIENT_ID, MAL_CLIENT_SECRECT and MAL_REDIRECT_URI in the .env file (Refer .env.safe).


